Function Reference/newuser notify siteadmin « WordPress Codex
-----------

Notifies the network admin that a new user has been activated.

Usage
-----

` <?php newuser_notify_siteadmin( $user_id ) ?> `

Parameters
----------

 `$user_id` 
:   ([*integer*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Integer "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*) The new user ID
    Default: *None*

Return Value
------------

 `` `(boolean)`{style="color:gray"} 
:   True on completion of email sent, False if registration notification
    is 'No' or if malformed user email.

Examples
--------

Notes
-----

Filter 'newuser\_notify\_siteadmin' to change the content of the
notification email. Filter function is passed \$msg (the email message
text), \$user (a WP\_User object for the new user)

Change Log
----------

Since: [MU](/Version_MU "Version MU")

Source File
-----------

`newuser_notify_siteadmin()` is located in
`wp-includes/ms-functions.php`

